docs.name: Caramelldansen (MOOND4WG Frenchcore Bootleg)
docs.description:
I'm really excited about this.
For context, I've probably started ~20+ maps in the past year.
How many have I finished?
1. And it sucked. I lose motivation extremely quickly so being able to finish this is exciting as heck for me.
Mapped completely by me, lit with Lolighter with some assistance from me.
If you come across this somehow, please try it. It would mean the world to me.
Please give feedback to me via the preview video or my discord: brgr_nezzled#8417
Preview video: https://youtu.be/pl-e0ZORsZY
<3
